Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,~OP~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.42,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I don't want nobody to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.17,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'll come and get you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.10,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I am always ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.75,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}So don't take all of the blame we were all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.91,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't take all of the weight. You always do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:35.83,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}There will always be something you cannot control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.96,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We will overcome. Your salvation has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:42.04,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}No signs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.97,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}No lights, such a mess all over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.21,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't kill your hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.03,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}You make me realize who l need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.97,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'll be there hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.79,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}They'll change you somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.71,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}So where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.52,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'll reach you by dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:09.51,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}The shadows appear, Illusions are born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.76,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}The fallen angels you run with don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:18.11,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}It is our pain that makes us all human after all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:21.18,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Torn old sepia photographs show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.20,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Our fragile precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.04,EnOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Must discard it, respond to the call
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.42,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我不愿任何人受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.17,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我将前来一会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.10,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我全副武装 时刻备战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.75,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}所以不必独自承担我们所推卸的责难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.91,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}不要独自承担一切 你却坚持如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:35.83,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}但并非一切皆在你掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.96,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我们会跨越难关 你的救赎已经到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:42.04,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.97,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无光 一片混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.21,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}别放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.03,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你让我明白我需要谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.97,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我一定会前来 好好等我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.79,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}他们将改变你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.71,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如今你又在何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.52,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我会于黎明前来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:09.51,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}光影乍现 幻象重重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.76,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你未察觉所背负的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:18.11,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}就是我们作为人类所经历的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:21.18,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}撕裂褪色的老照片所展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.20,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我们脆弱可贵的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.04,ChOP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}定要将其抛弃 响应召唤
